<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>救生艇新闻：博客——保护人类</title><link>https://lifeboat.com/blog/</link><description></description><lastBuildDate>Fri, 13 Mar 2026 12:37:22 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>“杰作”小鼠研究表明肠道微生物可以促进记忆丧失</title><link>https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/03/tour-de-force-mouse-study-shows-a-gut-microbe-can-promote-memory-loss</link><description>关于衰老为何会损害记忆力，科学家们有很多想法。大脑血流量减少、大脑体积缩小以及神经修复系统故障都被归咎于这一问题。现在，对小鼠的新研究指出了另一个可能的罪魁祸首：肠道中的微生物。 &lt;img src="https://lifeboat.com/blog.images/tour-de-force-mouse-study-shows-a-gut-microbe-can-promote-memory-loss.jpg" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Fri, 13 Mar 2026 12:37:20 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/03/tour-de-force-mouse-study-shows-a-gut-microbe-can-promote-memory-loss</guid></item><item><title>衰老通过激活综合应激反应促进转移</title><link>https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/03/ageing-promotes-metastasis-via-activation-of-the-integrated-stress-response</link><description>衰老重新编程了 KRAS 驱动的肺腺癌的进化轨迹，限制了原发性肿瘤的生长，同时通过整合应激反应的表观遗传激活促进了转移性扩散，并且揭示了老年患者的治疗机会。 &lt;img src="https://lifeboat.com/blog.images/ageing-promotes-metastasis-via-activation-of-the-integrated-stress-response.jpg" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Fri, 13 Mar 2026 12:22:20 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/03/ageing-promotes-metastasis-via-activation-of-the-integrated-stress-response</guid></item><item><title>单环充当光子分子</title><link>https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/03/a-single-ring-performs-as-a-photonic-molecule</link><description>一种新型环形光谐振器可以完成通常需要至少两个环的工作。&lt;img src="https://lifeboat.com/blog.images/a-single-ring-performs-as-a-photonic-molecule2.jpg" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Fri, 13 Mar 2026 12:07:20 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/03/a-single-ring-performs-as-a-photonic-molecule</guid></item><item><title>一种新型超硬材料</title><link>https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/03/a-new-superhard-material</link><description>在脆性材料的原子晶格中植入空位可以增加其韧性和硬度。&lt;img src="https://lifeboat.com/blog.images/a-new-superhard-material2.jpg" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Fri, 13 Mar 2026 11:52:20 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/03/a-new-superhard-material</guid></item><item><title>酷量子位可以更快地做出决策</title><link>https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/03/cool-qubits-make-faster-decisions</link><description>经典机器学习使从材料科学到医学成像的多个物理子领域受益。在量子计算机上实施机器学习算法可以将其用途扩展到更复杂的问题和本质上是量子的数据集。维也纳技术大学的 Nayeli Rodríguez-Briones 和韩国延世大学的 Daniel Park 现在提出了一种受热力学启发的协议，可以使量子机器学习技术更加高效。&lt;img src="https://lifeboat.com/blog.images/cool-qubits-make-faster-decisions2.jpg" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Fri, 13 Mar 2026 11:37:20 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/03/cool-qubits-make-faster-decisions</guid></item><item><title>宁静的银河岛屿：“小红点”可能酿造了生命的基石</title><link>https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/03/galactic-islands-of-tranquility-little-red-dots-may-have-brewed-lifes-building-blocks</link><description>天文学家发现，银河系的核心和宇宙中最早的原星系都有一个令人惊讶的特征：它们在严酷的辐射下异常平静。这种宁静不仅仅是一种宇宙的好奇心；它可能对于形成提供生命成分的复杂分子至关重要。 &lt;img src="https://lifeboat.com/blog.images/galactic-islands-of-tranquility-little-red-dots-may-have-brewed-lifes-building-blocks.jpg" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Fri, 13 Mar 2026 11:22:20 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/03/galactic-islands-of-tranquility-little-red-dots-may-have-brewed-lifes-building-blocks</guid></item><item><title>非对称自旋扭矩解锁反铁磁存储器的确定性控制</title><link>https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/03/asymmetric-spin-torque-unlocks-deterministic-control-of-antiferromagnetic-memory</link><description>中国科学院合肥物质科学研究院邵定富研究员团队提出了一种通用机制，可实现共线反铁磁体的确定性电控制，克服了反铁磁自旋电子学长期存在的瓶颈。该研究发表在《物理评论快报》上。 &lt;img src="https://lifeboat.com/blog.images/asymmetric-spin-torque-unlocks-deterministic-control-of-antiferromagnetic-memory2.jpg" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Fri, 13 Mar 2026 11:07:20 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/03/asymmetric-spin-torque-unlocks-deterministic-control-of-antiferromagnetic-memory</guid></item><item><title>手掌大小的超导磁体达到42特斯拉，可与世界上最大的超导磁体相媲美</title><link>https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/03/palm-sized-superconducting-magnet-achieves-42-tesla-rivaling-the-worlds-biggest</link><description>当我们想到粒子加速器或 NMR（核磁共振）中使用的强力磁铁时，我们经常会想到笨重的机器，有时有建筑物那么大。但在物理学上取得了非凡的突破，苏黎世联邦理工学院的科学家们创造出了小到可以放在手掌中的磁铁，但其威力却足以与世界上一些最强大的磁铁相媲美。 &lt;img src="https://lifeboat.com/blog.images/palm-sized-superconducting-magnet-achieves-42-tesla-rivaling-the-worlds-biggest2.jpg" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Fri, 13 Mar 2026 10:52:20 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/03/palm-sized-superconducting-magnet-achieves-42-tesla-rivaling-the-worlds-biggest</guid></item><item><title>发现具有冻结水能力的神奇真菌</title><link>https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/03/fantastic-fungi-found-with-ability-to-freeze-water</link><description>真菌会影响天气吗？事实证明，他们只是可能。包括弗吉尼亚理工大学的王晓峰和鲍里斯·A·维纳泽在内的一个国际研究小组发现了可以在零下高温下催化冰形成的真菌蛋白的特性。该研究发表在《科学进展》上。这一发现的一个潜在应用可能是改造天气。 &lt;img src="https://lifeboat.com/blog.images/fantastic-fungi-found-with-ability-to-freeze-water.jpg" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Fri, 13 Mar 2026 10:37:20 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/03/fantastic-fungi-found-with-ability-to-freeze-water</guid></item><item><title>从物理学的角度看待全球贸易</title><link>https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/03/seeing-global-trade-through-the-lens-of-physics</link><description>复杂性科学中心 (CSH) 的新研究表明了为什么广泛使用的衡量经济复杂性的算法会产生值得信赖的结果，以及这些工具如何使生态学、社会科学和代理人工智能等不同领域受益。该论文发表在《Physical Review E》杂志上。&lt;img src="https://lifeboat.com/blog.images/seeing-global-trade-through-the-lens-of-physics.jpg" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Fri, 13 Mar 2026 10:22:20 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/03/seeing-global-trade-through-the-lens-of-physics</guid></item></channel></rss>